President Obama has nominated William N. Nettles to be the US Attorney for the District of South Carolina. Nettles is currently an attorney at Sanders & Nettles LLC in Columbia, South Carolina. President Obama praised Nettles' distinguished and impressive legal career, expressing confidence in his ability to serve the people of South Carolina with distinction. Nettles has been practicing law since 1992 and has worked as a solo practitioner and partner in various law firms before joining Sanders & Nettles LLC in 2005. He began his legal career as an attorney in the Richland County Office of the Public Defender. Nettles graduated from The Citadel and the Widener University School of Law.